				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$\sim 1700$\end{document} km s−1 was well observed by SOHO/LASCO and STEREO-A/COR2, both positioned west of PSP (Cohen et al. 2021b). STEREO-A/EUVI also observed an EUV wave propagating away from the source at ∼500\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
